{
  "texts": [
    "AI polling, however, may put your privacy at risk.",
    "We have argued that when it comes to inputs, the collection and storage of data, technologies such as 'differential privacy' and generative deep learning are privacypreserving.",
    "When it comes to outputs, the privacy risks generated by the granularity of predictions is outweighed, in our view, by the significant gain of voters' knowledge highlighted above.",
    "We construe political privacy as protective of autonomy and have argued at length that AI polling enhances autonomous choice, all things considered.",
    "Besides the privacy risk, there is the alleged risk of manipulation."
  ]
}